text: Avdotyino () is a rural locality (a village) in Kashinskoye Rural Settlement of Volokolamsky District, Moscow Oblast, Russia. The population was 9 as of 2010. == Geography == The village is located 5 km north-east from Volokolamsk. == References == Category:Rural localities in Moscow Oblast
title: Avdotyino, Volokolamsky District, Moscow Oblast
